acioli" title=3D"Luca Pacioli">Luca Pacioli</a>;<sup id=3D"cite_ref-Pacioli=
_4-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Golden_r=
atio#cite_note-Pacioli-4"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>3<span class=
