rence"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Golden_ratio#cite_note-sima=
nek-86"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>80<span class=3D"cite-bracket"=
>]</span></a></sup>
</p><p><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Salvador_Dal%C3%AD" title=
=3D"Salvador Dal=C3=AD">Salvador Dal=C3=AD</a>, influenced by the works of =
<a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matila_Ghyka" title=3D"Matila Ghyk=
a">Matila Ghyka</a>,<sup id=3D"cite_ref-dalidimension_87-0" class=3D"refere=
nce"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Golden_ratio#cite_note-dalidi=
mension-87"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>81<span class=3D"cite-brac=
