upper</a></i>. The dimensions of the canvas are a golden rectangle. A huge =
dodecahedron, in perspective so that edges appear in golden ratio to one an=
other, is suspended above and behind <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wi=
ki/Jesus" title=3D"Jesus">Jesus</a> and dominates the composition.<sup id=
=3D"cite_ref-livio_plus_84-1" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wik=
ipedia.org/wiki/Golden_ratio#cite_note-livio_plus-84"><span class=3D"cite-b=
racket">[</span>78<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D=
"cite_ref-hunt_gilkey_88-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikip=
edia.org/wiki/Golden_ratio#cite_note-hunt_gilkey-88"><span class=3D"cite-br=
acket">[</span>82<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p><p>A statistical study on 565 works of art of different great painters,=
